author: DryRun
body: Adds monitoring plots for HF TP TDC cut: efficiency of cut vs. ieta vs iphi and ieta. Also adds the numerator and denominator of the efficiency calculation (i.e. data TP occupancy / emulated TP occupancy with no TDC cut).
title: HCALDQM: Add monitoring for HF TP TDC cut (10_1_X)
